{"hc1c19e80gd3dbg4d0aga220ge1f5a1b0b011": ["((*more are coming*))", "419b560c-143e-e6d2-ef04-48a516daf7d9", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MyconidCircle_RapportSpores_WithCompanions.html", "bf49ac23-531c-a4dc-ce6e-40863ffeb919"], "h26a8e537g6ca0g4e52g9e21gd6fe1ad30203": ["Hush. Do you hear it?", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MyconidCircle_RapportSpores_WithCompanions.html", "40c91d02-f276-a1a2-1858-df5d1c99e733"], "h6fc6bbd8gde09g4a0egba6fg37b303729f5a": ["((*they're coming. <i>they're coming</i>*))", "419b560c-143e-e6d2-ef04-48a516daf7d9", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MyconidCircle_RapportSpores_WithCompanions.html", "55d08449-829a-90c1-f8ef-f30592e5275f"], "h396cbdb6g3ecbg4e8bgab70g7c9c1656f86d": ["Tell me I'm not imagining that voice.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MyconidCircle_RapportSpores_WithCompanions.html", "417ecc2c-8ff4-62b9-7338-1da5fbec5809"], "ha8ce9ea5gf4c7g40beg9248gc22b74fca26f": ["No. And it's unlike any I've yet heard.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MyconidCircle_RapportSpores_WithCompanions.html", "614dea3c-e50e-2725-7e11-52bffb21d647"], "hf3108b95g4d5fg409fgb9b8g2842ecd9c65d": ["((*they're coming. <i>you're coming</i>*))", "419b560c-143e-e6d2-ef04-48a516daf7d9", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MyconidCircle_RapportSpores_WithCompanions.html", "38545410-d202-e557-8f33-cb720c41190c"], "h807342f9g917fg47ecg9ed1gbeb570b32e27": ["Careful... if we can hear it, perhaps it can hear us...", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MyconidCircle_RapportSpores_WithCompanions.html", "10c1859d-8293-168c-8711-61dac868dd95"], "h37db8d08g0357g4a9cgb4a4ga20fce6e2796": ["No. Something's coming - and if it lives down here in the dark, it won't be anything good.", "2c76687d-93a2-477b-8b18-8a14b549304c", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MyconidCircle_RapportSpores_WithCompanions.html", "edc9e283-6323-10cd-a128-328f70b02171"], "h044c5fd8g9bcdg420fg8f63g5be5234baf3a": ["Hm. Perhaps we should strike one another, just to be sure.", "0de603c5-42e2-4811-9dad-f652de080eba", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MyconidCircle_RapportSpores_WithCompanions.html", "e6ff3190-bbc4-082c-4cd9-f42cb856fa45"], "h0e5e870cg1f59g44e6g9a20g9678673881da": ["No, someone's coming. And someone else wants us to know...", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MyconidCircle_RapportSpores_WithCompanions.html", "2640cf9c-5a9a-2466-0f48-ecaad04b0441"], "h04878319ga1f4g495fg9c10g597bae02a42f": ["If you are, I am. Think whatever it is can hear <i>us?</i>", "98b9a4da-d3af-494e-890b-c8ec85d3146d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MyconidCircle_RapportSpores_WithCompanions.html", "39717aac-bf0a-09d7-9c43-3b71ba912c55"], "h6293ac0egec2dg42b8g887ag1cdfcb6d0ee0": ["It said 'they're coming.' But... who?", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MyconidCircle_RapportSpores_WithCompanions.html", "00799744-61fb-1043-fde9-4ca4dbb824d6"], "h3100418bgc234g4354gbbe5g49f5906d1508": ["That's a myconid. And it's warning us...", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MyconidCircle_RapportSpores_WithCompanions.html", "ecee966d-d418-ca26-bf82-b144d10d2301"], "h47b5e644g37fbg4d61g9680ga1f18768b118": ["<i>Still your mind to this unusual voice.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MyconidCircle_RapportSpores_WithCompanions.html", "cb856c77-1f91-6338-14c3-ab8a08c28ac0"], "h308eb894gfe4bg4c01g8b46gefc0235a1f2d": ["Control your thoughts. It seems I'm not the only one listening.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MyconidCircle_RapportSpores_WithCompanions.html", "1f504f86-7de9-2594-2951-ff6bf845e3f8"], "h93881c0agc132g439fg8979g36c9ba7ef54d": ["((*they're coming. <i>you're coming</i>*))", "419b560c-143e-e6d2-ef04-48a516daf7d9", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MyconidCircle_RapportSpores_WithCompanions.html", "226b59e2-b412-900a-5b0f-f8c80bd9807b"], "hf87f5b78gb6e0g45d8gb1acgcd0efe1e8d41": ["Careful... if we can hear it, perhaps it can hear us...", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MyconidCircle_RapportSpores_WithCompanions.html", "8705d472-d8f9-fa1a-c493-cc97ea81c154"], "h10ddbccegf772g40d0gb9b8g8c24650061e9": ["This might be some devil's ploy. Don't listen to it.", "2c76687d-93a2-477b-8b18-8a14b549304c", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MyconidCircle_RapportSpores_WithCompanions.html", "4d55b1f0-63b8-725d-c855-9a5b6b90aedc"], "hb523b19fg1efbg408agab4bga0187489aabb": ["I tire of this noise. Let us trade blows, not <i>thoughts.</i>", "0de603c5-42e2-4811-9dad-f652de080eba", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MyconidCircle_RapportSpores_WithCompanions.html", "5582bb76-82cf-260d-abc4-d76705b61ba1"], "h7342a310g0e3fg406ag9f16gedb85ed523f8": ["You listen all you want - but it can get the hells out of my head.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MyconidCircle_RapportSpores_WithCompanions.html", "c8eaf099-8b5c-08dd-0145-33e901a9ab53"], "h7eb83055g7f21g432fgbf33ge1f4e7f8e093": ["Whoever it is can get out. <i>Now.</i>", "98b9a4da-d3af-494e-890b-c8ec85d3146d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MyconidCircle_RapportSpores_WithCompanions.html", "6d1e8ab9-010a-eaf7-d46f-4aaacf03180f"], "h0f116136g3668g45a0gb37ag6de74fbbfc70": ["It said 'they're coming.' But... who?", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MyconidCircle_RapportSpores_WithCompanions.html", "a4e943bc-2a32-a46b-86fc-bb4103278f29"], "h1a9f9077gd9d5g4f4dg8e9cg6f0aa5e83650": ["No, listen! A myconid... it's warning us.", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MyconidCircle_RapportSpores_WithCompanions.html", "bea942e8-2100-fb13-1f83-48270166bb72"], "h43d17b86gf888g413fg85feg2b68acfe15ab": ["Something is coming. Has a devil found me at last?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MyconidCircle_RapportSpores_WithCompanions.html", "f83f93d8-dfb8-9b2d-7498-3917639e9314"], "h2ba6b54ag593fg4200g891bg02a7d489dcc0": ["Then control your thoughts, lest your mind be exploited.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MyconidCircle_RapportSpores_WithCompanions.html", "90d371c8-3b4f-d568-6127-095b180a2810"], "haa9afe48g394dg4e8bgb9cfg8e1bd2a6b426": ["Such faculties of observation you possess! I'm ready, whatever's coming...", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MyconidCircle_RapportSpores_WithCompanions.html", "7fdf0f68-c315-4389-eca9-01560b7cc62b"], "h4f25f924ga5b3g464eg82f9gd9564bf63e12": ["Something's coming - and if it lives down here in the dark, it won't be anything good.", "2c76687d-93a2-477b-8b18-8a14b549304c", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MyconidCircle_RapportSpores_WithCompanions.html", "853dec31-91da-6827-8e34-6b1ad8bab5be"], "h31c2586bg6eafg4ec2gaedcg9d6f200bb20e": ["Then let us be the something good to meet it, hm?", "0de603c5-42e2-4811-9dad-f652de080eba", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MyconidCircle_RapportSpores_WithCompanions.html", "56ebac28-de49-c202-ee6f-775ca806683f"], "hd699e98eg95fdg402ega438g644337bbfdb5": ["It's never good news with a mysterious voice, is it? Always 'warning, demons', never 'warning, nymphs bathing nearby'.", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MyconidCircle_RapportSpores_WithCompanions.html", "0346447c-dbd3-8db5-89af-809e1ac6e3b6"], "h4e551109gf3a5g48e5g9c0bg1b83d14fa928": ["Claws out. Got it.", "98b9a4da-d3af-494e-890b-c8ec85d3146d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MyconidCircle_RapportSpores_WithCompanions.html", "cae0fc26-00aa-a3b0-59c8-0b842906b7fc"], "h7416c1c8g291dg49cbg90e3g5667a6106a28": ["Well, when a creepy voice says 'something's coming', it's never <i>good</i>, is it?", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MyconidCircle_RapportSpores_WithCompanions.html", "f5910c09-6e1d-ed93-5376-0cd0cc8d2bd2"], "hf3e140a0g7d35g490egaf1egc527d333dcc0": ["No devils here. That's a myconid. And it seems to be warning us...", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MyconidCircle_RapportSpores_WithCompanions.html", "31663500-f219-1caf-b053-5a8ab6931ab1"], "h38fd0aa1g58b8g48c6gb221g839bee21be7e": ["<i>Stay silent. Could Cazador have found you?</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MyconidCircle_RapportSpores_WithCompanions.html", "7f1b5220-5026-c835-59cb-6d9bf21aa0ae"], "ha8bdc3a2g8317g42a1g8fadg93aea95a92af": ["<i>You think of Shar - could she be speaking to you here at last, in the dark...?</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MyconidCircle_RapportSpores_WithCompanions.html", "0935f457-3454-74a0-255b-3237106faa73"], "h411c57a3g748bg4f2bg9013g931816568c8e": ["<i>Still your thoughts to this new voice.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MyconidCircle_RapportSpores_WithCompanions.html", "51a0fe65-5b29-d403-2997-f64ed7862da4"], "h5686f7dbg15adg4a16gbebdg002fa0cc3af8": ["<i>Pray for fortitude against the mental trespass.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MyconidCircle_RapportSpores_WithCompanions.html", "3511ec40-3ba9-22de-5293-35477aa903b9"], "hadbccdd0g1887g42e8ga34eg74b83ba0a77c": ["<i>Ignore the voice.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MyconidCircle_RapportSpores_WithCompanions.html", "1bf56fa6-32d1-b691-2e0b-0e5a56cfe889"], "hd4838bd3gdd64g4530g8beagdaef1bc1c186": ["That voice... what was that?", "3ed74f06-3c60-42dc-83f6-f034cb47c679", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MyconidCircle_RapportSpores_WithCompanions.html", "32f84061-2513-6e0e-7ef4-5c27bbd2fb02"], "hf3c72383gfdb0g4566g8052g5036fb442b10": ["What in the Nine Hells is <i>that</i>?", "2c76687d-93a2-477b-8b18-8a14b549304c", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MyconidCircle_RapportSpores_WithCompanions.html", "63452f61-4de2-63b7-61ba-ee41fceca811"], "h3c5cd3f0g088ag4e3bg9749gc2a851d79ce4": ["_", "0de603c5-42e2-4811-9dad-f652de080eba", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MyconidCircle_RapportSpores_WithCompanions.html", "1317648a-bc6b-27a5-801e-386aaafe485b"], "h949042d6gcc15g427ag85b5gda5d5d6571cc": ["Who - <i>what </i>in the Hells are you?", "c7c13742-bacd-460a-8f65-f864fe41f255", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MyconidCircle_RapportSpores_WithCompanions.html", "84616ff6-3ec4-b66d-5ba1-b2fb49b1ded6"], "hb7b2cb53g31d6g4ed1g9577g5c6697edfea7": ["What the ham?!", "98b9a4da-d3af-494e-890b-c8ec85d3146d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MyconidCircle_RapportSpores_WithCompanions.html", "320ccbf3-170e-ff8b-09f7-f1966cab7329"], "hee3f1b1ag577eg4bb7g84a7g7fc75a864cbd": ["Tell me you hear that voice.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MyconidCircle_RapportSpores_WithCompanions.html", "90ec2a83-482f-9253-9031-c6f7278e1062"], "hc7f3eb4dgc4c1g45c8g893eg67283848ceb2": ["That voice... Do you hear it too?", "ad9af97d-75da-406a-ae13-7071c563f604", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Underdark\\UND_MyconidCircle_RapportSpores_WithCompanions.html", "5d0245d0-43e1-79c1-3a19-29676187f590"]}